igh-Tech nurses, etc.)<\/li><li>Immediate support for strike and crisis nurse staffing<\/li><li>Ability to bolster services during high-demand periods, like summer months<\/li><li>Complete onboarding services freeing your HR department to focus on daily operations<\/li><li>EMR training and support for nurse staffing during EMR conversions<\/li><li>Billing and payroll support for temporary nurse staffing<\/li><li>Telehealth capabilities including onsite language translation services<\/li><li>Healthcare leadership recruitment, including Directors of Nursing<\/li><\/ul><p>\u00a0<\/p><p><strong>Our expertise in nursing covers, but is not limited to:<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Per-diem nurse placements<\/li><li>Temporary nurse staffing (locum tenens)<\/li><li>Critical staffing and rapid response assignments<\/li><li>Permanent nurse placements<\/li><li>Interim nurse manager or nurse director placements<\/li><\/ul><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>We excel in filling demanding and hard-to-fill positions, promptly and successfully addressing four, twelve, or twenty-six-week healthcare staffing gaps.<\/p><p>Pre-Screening We exclusively recruit and place qualified and experienced nurses, streamlining the hiring process and saving your valuable time and resources typically spent on advertising, interviewing, reference checks, and training.<\/p><p>Every clinician at Tenderhearts Healthcare Staffing undergoes meticulous vetting and continuous education, ensuring compliance and readiness. This approach saves our clients time and resources typically associated with hiring and training.<\/p><p><strong>Detailed Screening includes:<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Professional License Verification<\/li><li>Current BLS Certification<\/li><li>Employment Eligibility Checks<\/li><li>Skills Set Evaluation<\/li><li>Background Checks<\/li><li>Drug Screening<\/li><li>Supervisory Reference Checks<\/li><li>Health Assessments<\/li><li>NPDB Review<\/li><li>End-of-Assignment Evaluations<\/li><li>DMV Screening<\/li><li>Annual TB 